        "subject": "LU-5355 tests: Unknown mac type 'achinefile'",
        "message": "LU-5355 tests: Unknown mac type 'achinefile'\n\nAccording to the mpirun man page, -machinefile should be allowed, but\n--machinefile is also valid, so at the very least, it will help\nnarrow down where the error message is coming from.\n\nUpdate large-lun.sh to use ${MACHINEFILE_OPTION} instead of\nhard-coding the parameter.\n\nTest-Parameters: testlist=parallel-scale\nSigned-off-by: Joshua Kugler <joshua.kugler@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I9493c25f564dd61c04bf4f2bdb598b7ffa576273\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
